Those that have completed Witcher 3: Wild Hunt know that it&rsquo;s sadly the end of Geralt&rsquo;s Story. Fortunately CD Projekt Red has confirmed that it will not be the end of the franchise! CEO of CD Projekt Red Adam Kicinski said that Witcher 4 is confirmed and will be coming in the future!<br />
<br />
&ldquo;It&rsquo;s too early to talk about it, but it&rsquo;s not like we&rsquo;re forgetting about this brand,&rdquo; he said on Polish TV station TVN24 BiS. &ldquo;It wouldn&rsquo;t be fair towards the fans. We work within this universe for over a dozen years now and I don&rsquo;t think it&rsquo;s going to be the end of it.&rdquo;

